description:
THE INTERACTIVE APP FOR KIDS
Lingokids is the fun, safe, educational kids learning app that toddlers and children aged 2–8 love—and parents trust! Packed with over 3000 shows, songs, coloring games, cooking games, and interactive activities, it lets your child play, learn, and grow at their own pace. This is screen time for girls and boys you can feel good about.

LINGOKIDS NOW HAS DISNEY ACTIVITIES!
Your kid can now play brand-new Disney Mickey & Friends, Disney Moana and Disney Frozen-themed activities. All fun, all edutaining—and all on the Playlearning™ app kids love! 
From math to literacy to creativity, help your kid practice at their own pace with activities featuring beloved Disney characters like Anna, Elsa and Olaf, Moana and Maui, and Mickey Mouse, Donald Duck and Goofy.
Because when activities are this edutaining, they become something your kid truly loves!

5 REASONS LINGOKIDS IS GUILT-FREE FOR FAMILIES
Made by parents & educators
Loved by toddlers, preschoolers, and elementary school kids
kidSAFE® certified & 100% ad-free
More than 30 global awards
Over 3000 fun kids games and activities to play!

INTERACTIVE ACTIVITIES
Your kids can explore over 3000 interactive games, coloring games, and toddler-friendly challenges covering 650+ learning objectives—all through play! Subjects include math, literacy, science, engineering, art, music, and more. Kids can move at their own pace through a curated curriculum using fun toddler games, books, videos, and songs. Perfect games for your 2,3,4,5,6,7,8 year olds!


PLAYLEARNING™ METHOD
At Lingokids, we believe learning sticks when it’s wrapped in fun. Our Playlearning™ method inspires toddlers and kids to discover the world naturally—through play, repetition, and curiosity. From coloring and games to movement, stories, and songs, every interaction builds real skills.

FEATURED BRANDS & CHARACTERS
Your kids can play with familiar favorites like Blippi and Pocoyo. Plus, brand-new activities featuring beloved Disney characters all available inside the Lingokids app. And discover activities created with trusted names like NASA and Oxford University Press.

Many families may already know Lingokids from our videos on YouTube and YouTube Kids, where over 3 million subscribers enjoy our playful, edutaining content. Now, those same kids can keep learning through fun toddler games and interactive activities inside the app.

SUBJECTS, THEMES & LEVELS THAT GROW WITH YOUR CHILD
Reading & Literacy: Build phonics, writing, and reading confidence.
Math & Engineering: Strengthen number sense, addition, subtraction, and logical thinking.
Science & Tech: Introduce biology, chemistry, coding, robotics and NASA-powered activities.
Music & Art: Play with rhythm, sound, and creativity in music + coloring games.
Social-Emotional Learning: Practice empathy, expression, and mindfulness.
History & Geography: Spark curiosity about the world and its stories.
Physical Activity: Fun stretches, yoga, and movement songs keep toddlers engaged!

WHY UPGRADE TO LINGOKIDS PLUS?
Unlimited access to 3000+ toddler games, coloring games, and activities
Covers 650+ learning goals across subjects and life skills
Expert-designed lessons for boys and girls aged 2–8
Lingokids activities featuring Disney, Blippi, Pocoyo, NASA and Oxford University Press content
Progress reports, parent community, and up to 4 child profiles
100% ad-free, with no in-app purchases
Play online or offline—anywhere, anytime!

Subscriptions automatically renew each month 24-hours before the end of the current period and your iTunes account will be charged unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period. You can turn off auto-renew any time from within the app. Any unused portion of a free trial will be forfeited if you purchase a subscription.

developer: Bimi Boo Kids Learning Games for Toddlers FZ LLC
description:
Learning numbers for kids is an educational game for preschoolers. The game will allow boys and girls to learn numbers 1 to 20 while playing entertaining mini-games. Learning numbers features over 100 educational activities for your child to enjoy. The game will also help children to develop important basic skills such as creativity, motor skills, coordination, attention and memory.

Each number in our educational game for kids has its own story. This makes the game process diverse and exciting for children. The game includes essential learning activities such as number tracing, math and counting.

Learning numbers is an educational game that is designed for kindergarten and preschool kids ages 2, 3, 4, 5 and 6. The game will teach your child to identify numbers, count them, write them and pronounce them correctly. The learning process is easy and extremely engaging.

Our toddler game allows kids to learn numbers in a variety of languages: English, Spanish, French, German, Italian, Russian, Portuguese, Turkish, Greek, Dutch, Danish, Swedish, Norwegian, Finnish, Chinese, Japanese, Korean, Czech, Polish, Romanian, Hungarian, Ukrainian, Hindi, Croatian and Slovenian.

Features:
- Number learning for kids
- Tracing and counting from 1 to 20
- Math game for preschoolers
- Learning numbers in 17 different languages
- Over 100 educational activities for both girls and boys
- Kids number games with cute animals
- Numbers 1, 2 and 3 are available for free
Ages: 2, 3, 4 or 5 years old pre-kindergarten and kindergarten children.

You will never find annoying ads inside our app. We are always glad to receive your feedback and suggestions.

Trusted by over 40 million learners worldwide.

TellaNote – AI Note Taker & Study Assistant

Stay focused in class. TellaNote is the AI-powered note-taking app that captures lectures, transcribes audio into clean study notes, and turns them into flashcards, quizzes, and study guides — all in seconds. Perfect for college, university, and high school students who want to learn faster, stress less, and ace exams.

Capture (Live or Later)

One-tap lecture recorder for in-person classes, seminars, labs, and study groups

Import audio or video later (missed classes, recorded meetings, or review sessions)

Add voice notes, highlights, and timestamps/bookmarks while recording to instantly revisit key moments

Fast, accurate speech-to-text optimized for classroom audio

Turn Audio Into Notes

Instant AI notes with clear headings, bullets, and concise summaries

Auto-highlights definitions, key terms, formulas, and examples

Smart sections that mirror the flow of the lecture

Search across all notes and recordings in seconds

Consistent, organized formatting that’s easy to study

Study Faster With Built-In Tools

Flashcard maker: one tap to generate study-ready flashcards (supports spaced repetition)

Practice quizzes: test yourself before exams with AI-generated quizzes

Study guides: auto-compile polished study guides from your notes for finals or midterms

Organize Your Semester

Class folders keep notes, flashcards, and quizzes together

View by course, date, or topic — no more scattered files

Works across iPhone and Web so you can record on your phone and review on your laptop

Your Personal Class AI

Per-class AI chatbots trained on your uploaded materials

Ask follow-ups, get clarifications, and quiz yourself on difficult concepts

Quick refreshers before class or exams

Designed for Real Students

Made for fast talkers and dense slides where it is hard to keep up

Missed class? Import a recording and still get structured notes

Clear summaries that reduce overwhelm (helpful for ESL and ADHD)

Clean, simple interface that keeps you motivated to study

Privacy and Control

You control your data — delete recordings and notes anytime

Secure and reliable syncing across devices

Why Tela Note?

Telenote combines an AI note taker, lecture recorder, flashcard maker, quiz generator, and study guide builder into one app. No more juggling multiple tools — just one streamlined study companion built for students who want better grades with less stress.

How a Typical Lecture Looks in TellaNote

Tap Record and stay focused on the lecture

Drop a timestamp when the professor says, “This will be on the exam”

Stop recording and instantly get organized AI notes

Generate flashcards and a quiz for your next study block

Before the test, compile a study guide and review with your class AI

Subscription and Pricing

TellaNote is free to download with limited features. A subscription is required to access the main app and unlock AI notes, flashcards, quizzes, study guides, and class AI chat.

Weekly, monthly, and annual plans available

Payment charged to your Apple ID at confirmation of purchase

Explore and experience the fun and super cute world of the Dream Ice Castle with Princess Pippi!
Open up "Pippi World :Princess Avatar" unlock different locations, dress up various styles and sizes of princesses and princes, and interact with countless items, furniture, and characters. Step into this mystical world and create your own princess story in the magnificent, dreamy castle!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

A Day in the Life of a Princess
Ever wondered what it's like to live as a princess? Wake up in a luxurious princess bed, take a bath in an elegant tub, shop at your exclusive boutique, then enjoy afternoon tea at the dessert shop... In this beautiful ice world, you are the star! You can do anything you want, with no limits or restrictions, and the adventure never ends! Dive into this vast and mysterious world with your friends and family!

Create New Characters
Unleash your endless imagination and create any character you like! Choose from hundreds of unique facial features, outfits, hairstyles, accessories, jewelry, and wings, make up and makeover to make them one-of-a-kind! Do you prefer a character that's elegant, glamorous, cute, or quirky? Or maybe stylish, handsome, or even wacky? Your creativity brings them to life, giving each character a unique personality and charm!
Of course, the characters you create can also experience all the activities in Pippi World! They can interact with all the items, explore every location, and discover the magic and surprises hidden around every corner. Make your mark in this world by leaving unique footprints of your adventures!

Explore Everything
Create unique interactive stories! You can be a princess or even the hairstylist at the salon – why not? It's all up to you!
Find all the hidden plots and Easter eggs! Where's the key to the treasure chest? What cute things will hatch from the eggs? Dive into the game and explore!
Solve all the puzzles! Clues on the notes will guide you – but where are the notes? I'm sure you can find them!
And what else is special? That's for you to discover when you enter Pippi World!

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

"Pippi World :Princess Avatar" isn't just a regular dress up games, princess games, or doll games. In this rich virtual world, players can develop important skills like creativity, exploration, imagination, and design, as well as problem-solving abilities in real life! Download "Pippi World :Princess Avatar" now, and create your own princess story in this adorable game!

developer: HELLOTALK FOREIGN LANGUAGE EXCHANGE LEARNING TALK CHAT APP
description:
Practice languages with native speakers on HelloTalk! We recently introduced HelloTalk Live and Voiceroom - interactive language and culture events to help you master languages through the content you love! 

HelloTalk, the original language exchange app, connects you with native speakers to practice languages (English, Japanese, Korean, Spanish, French, Mandarin Chinese, Portuguese, German, Italian, Russian, Arabic, Turkish, Hindi, Indonesian, Thai, Vietnamese and 160+ more) for FREE! 

HelloTalk equips you with learning tools such as translation and instant captions so you can learn by chatting with native speakers. Learn languages from locals around the world through livestreams and Voicerooms. Connect with expert hosts to discuss interesting topics with language partners in the learning community! 

Why HelloTalk? 

► Real language learning atmosphere 
Whether you're focused on a widely spoken language or a less common one, HelloTalk caters to your needs. The system smartly matches you based on your native language and proficiency, while allowing you to filter ideal language partners according to various criteria such as age, location, and gender. Plus, with built-in translation and transliteration tools, you can communicate confidently without any language barriers.

► A powerful tool for sharpening your language skills
Acquiring new words through conversations with native speakers is more effective than rigid memorization. Whether you're a student preparing for exams like the CET, GRE, TOEFL, IELTS, planning to study abroad, or a professional seeking career advancement through language skills, HelloTalk offers native speakers who match your proficiency level for engaging interactions and valuable learning experiences.

► Immersive multi-person language chat rooms
If you choose to learn Spanish, for example, every Voiceroom you enter on HelloTalk gathers Spanish learners and Spanish native speakers from around the world to discuss interesting topics. Here, only your voice needs to be heard, creating a comfortable, introvert-friendly atmosphere. Here, sharing mutual interests allows everyone to freely express themselves and share personal experiences, fostering both language intuition and authentic expression skills.
